HIDDEN TRICKS AND TIPS

BETWEEN includes 1 and 10 if you want to include only the middle men use >1 AND <10

If you have a long list of campaign names, use IN much quicker and easier than multiple OR

Comparison operators ignore NULL cells . If you want to find people with phone numbers not entered you ned to use WHERE phone IS NULL

Text sensitivity: make sure everything is standardised before comparing (use UPPER, LOWER, TRIMM) if needed.

NOT IN your exclusion list must not contain NULL
